{"tid":1998470,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有個毒撚廢老同事帶飯返公司食 俾我地笑到面黃","createTime":"2020-05-02T11:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T13:27:14.000Z","uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"255b73b37d97cd53b8d6b680cd2f4136f6dfab9d","tid":1998470,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:55:57.000Z","msg":"有個毒撚老坑50+同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一日返工 我地諗住叫埋佢一齊出去食啦<br />\n<br />\n點知佢細細講咁講話佢帶咗飯打算叮熱黎食，<br />\n<br />\n我地成班呆撚咗，咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有廢老帶飯返黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢答：「唔...唔係呀，想草錢呀⋯⋯屋企人失業冇飯開⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗買乜咁巴閉要草錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n之後我地拎咗佢裝飯個袋，<br />\n<br />\n拎個飯盒出黎打開個盒，<br />\n<br />\n將佢啲垃圾餸掉曬落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢眼濕濕咁用手執返啲飯同餸落個盒度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家D廢老真係唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fea9808ca4ccb3ffd1fa30193c1d0abd8f0b1e7","tid":1998470,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667b3ccfd4ad9b1aa5116fcb897c89e62d0cadb3","tid":1998470,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:29:31.000Z","msg":"消滅廢老 由我做起<img src=\